english, "favour", "favor", queststatus(417) >= expr(200) -> "Ronagan is delighted with you and your path."
english, "favour", "favor", queststatus(417) >= expr(150) -> "Ronagan is charmed by you."
english, "favour", "favor", queststatus(417) >= expr(100) -> "Ronagan is happy with you."
